org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.plan

Class VectorPTFInfo

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.hadoop.hive.ql.plan.VectorPTFInfo

  • public class VectorPTFInfo
extends Object
    VectorGroupByAggregrationInfo. A convenience data structure that has information needed to vectorize reduce sink. It is created by the Vectorizer when it is determining whether it can specialize so the information doesn't have to be recreated again and against by the VectorPTFOperator's constructors and later during execution.
